Version 1.0.1
=============

Released 2007-Oct-20

Small bugfix release, no new features:
 * Bugfix: Problem with endianess on Mac OS X PPC machines.  Thanks to Niall Moran for reporting it.
 * Bugfix: Possible lseek() issue on files bigger than 4GB.
 * Corrected license in endian.{c,h}

